title: Dionne Argyropoulos
text: Dionne (she/her) is in the final stages of completing her PhD in the Genetic Epidemiology of Plasmodium falciparum malaria in high burden settings. Aside from the endless curiosity that sparks her joy in research, Dionne is true to her Melbourne-Greek heritage by being a Eurovision connoisseur and a foodie.
